Private Sub DetailReport_AfterPrint(ByVal sender As Object, ByVal e As System.EventArgs) xrPortes.Visible = False xrFretes.Visible = False xrSeguros.Visible = False xrLabel42.Visible = True End Sub
Private Sub DetailReport_BeforePrint(ByVal sender As Object, ByVal e As System.ComponentModel.CancelEventArgs)
xrSeguros.Visible = (xrLabel8.text = "X000003") xrFretes.Visible = (xrLabel8.text = "X000002") xrPortes.Visible = (xrLabel8.text = "X000001")
xrLabel42.Visible = (xrLabel8.Text <> "X000001") AND (xrLabel8.Text <> "X000002") AND (xrLabel8.Text <> "X000003")
End Sub
